*<div id="solrclient.getbyid" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">SolrClient::getById</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PECL solr &gt;= 2.2.0)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">SolrClient::getById</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">Get Document By Id. Utilizes Solr Realtime Get (RTG)</span></p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-solrclient.getbyid-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="modifier">public</span> <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>SolrClient::getById</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">string</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">$id</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/class.solrqueryresponse.php" class="type SolrQueryResponse" style="color:#EAB766">SolrQueryResponse</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">    Get Document By Id. Utilizes Solr Realtime Get (RTG).  </p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-solrclient.getbyid-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <dl>       <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">id</span></dt>    <dd>     <span>      Document ID     </span>    </dd>     </dl> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-solrclient.getbyid-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/class.solrqueryresponse.php" class="type SolrQueryResponse" style="color:#EAB766">SolrQueryResponse</a></span>  </p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></